UnitStabilityPool::setLiquidationManager
└── when called by non-governance
│   └── it reverts


UnitStabilityPool::deposit
├── when amount is zero
│   └── it reverts
└── when pool is empty
    ├── it updates total deposits
    ├── it mints shares one-to-one
    └── it updates the user's deposit balance


UnitStabilityPool::withdraw
└── when amount exceeds current deposit balance after offset
    ├── it reverts
    └── it allows withdrawing the reduced balance


UnitStabilityPool::offset
├── when called by non-liquidationManager
│   └── it reverts
└── when called by liquidationManager
    ├── it burns pool deposits
    ├── it reduces depositor LPUSD balances pro-rata
    ├── it accrues collateral rewards pro-rata
    └── it receives LP collateral


UnitStabilityPool::claim
├── when user has accrued collateral rewards
│   ├── it transfers LP collateral to the user
│   └── it clears the user's claimable balance
└── when a user deposits after rewards exist
    ├── it does not give the new depositor past rewards
    └── it preserves earlier depositors' accrued rewards
